          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Supporting Teachers and Safe Students Act</strong></p> <p>This bill allows state and local educational agencies to use certain federal funds for activities&nbsp;related&nbsp;to school safety, including professional development for school personnel in mental-health awareness and violence prevention.</p>]]></text>
